## 4. Resource Types
### Management Zone

```hcl
resource "dynatrace_management_zone_v2" "production" {
  name = "Production"

  rules {
    type    = "SERVICE"
    enabled = true

    conditions {
      condition {
        key {
          type      = "STATIC"
          attribute = "SERVICE_TAGS"
        }
        tag {
          operator = "EQUALS"
          negate   = false
          value {
            context = "CONTEXTLESS"
            key     = "environment"
            value   = "production"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

### Auto-Tagging Rule

```hcl
resource "dynatrace_autotag_v2" "application" {
  name = "Application"

  rules {
    type         = "SERVICE"
    enabled      = true
    value_format = "{Service:DetectedName}"
    conditions   = []
  }
}
```

